name: Reuben Rollups
author: SHANNONY
summary: Delicious, not terribly authentic, refreshing wraps - a great way to dress up leftover meat! Try shredded pork or steak! These wraps can be dressed up or down as the situation warrants.
directions: Warm tortillas in microwave to soften; keep covered with a damp towel
Spread one side of each tortilla with 2 tablespoons Russian-style salad dressing
Arrange equal amounts of the cole slaw in the center of each tortilla
Sprinkle equal amounts corned beef over the cole slaw
Top with equal amounts of Swiss cheese
Tightly roll tortillas around the fillings
Chill in the refrigerator until serving
